    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad nu wiꞥſch bij beidſis ar Saulu runnaht/ tad fatweenojahs Ionataxa Sir̄ds ar to Sir̄di Dahwida/ un Jonatans eenihleja winnu/ ka tawn paschu Dwehfeli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sauls nehme winnu tai patc̄a Deena/ un ne likke to fawa Tehwa Namā atgreestees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ionatans darrija ween Derribu ar Dahwidu/ tapehz ka wiꞥſch to mihleja ka fawu paschu Dwehfeli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ionatans nozehme fawu Mehteli/ kas winnam btja/ un dewe to Dahwidam/ ir fawas Drehbes/ ir fawu paschu Sohbtnu/ un fawu Stohpu/ un fawu Johstu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Dahwids iṣgahje wiṣfur/ kury Sauls winnu fuhttja/ un turrejahs gudri/ un Sauls eezeſhle to pahr teem Karra-Wihreent/ un tas patikke labbi wiṣteem Landim/ ir Saula Kalpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tee nu nahze/ un Dahwids atgreeschs no ta Wilistexa Kauschanas/ tad iṣgahje tahs Seewas no teen Psilſahteem ar Dseetinahn un Stabulehm tam\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs Seewas spehledamas dseedaja prett ween ohtru un faẓtija : Sauls irr tuhſtochus nokawis/ bet Dahwidesmitstuhſtochus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apskaitahs Sauls tohti/ un fchi Walloda ne patikkwinnam/ un faẓtija : Tee irr Dahwidam defimits tuhſtochus dewufchi/ un man irr tee tuhſtochus dewufchi/ teec̄ham ta Wallitiba wehl winnam taps.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sauls Dahwidu niknuſraudsijahs no tahs Deenas/ un joprohjam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ohtrā Deena/ kad tas taunajs Deewa Gars pahr Saulu nahze/ un tas faẓtija Pra-weefchu Mahzibn fawa pascha Namā/ tad spehleja Dahwids artawn Rohku ikDeenas/un Saulam bija Schkehps Rohkā/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sauls mette to Schkehpu/ un dohmaja : Es Dahwidu pee Seenas nodurſchu. Un Dahwids nowehrſchs diwkahrt no winna Waiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sauls bihjajahs preekſch Dahwida/ jo tas KUNgs btja ar winnu/ un btja no Saulala atſtahjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz atſtahdinaja Sauls winnu no fevis/ un darrija to par weenu Ahwerſtn/ un tas iṣgahje un eegahje preekſch to Kaunschn Azzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids turrejahs Bbbb gudri\n"
    }
  ],
